FT  07 JUL 94 / UK Company News: Melville completes exhibition sale
Melville Group has completed the sale of its UK exhibition services
activities, trading under the name Melville Exhibition Services, to
Estatepark Enterprises for up to Pounds 11.4m.
The consideration comprises Pounds 9.4m cash, Pounds 1m in loan notes and a
deferred element of Pounds 1m payable in certain circumstances if the
purchaser's share capital is sold or listed.
Melville directors said the sale was a 'significant step' in completing the
company's full restructuring - the shares will remain suspended.
